  <diagram id="HGtqnhsRsf4_-v-mt_0W" name="Page-4">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1325" dy="767" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="7JGCFXET-1jq0NP8rzOu-2" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;align=left;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Large Retail Company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Computer parts and electronics&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Stores, 3 yr ago 50 stores, in us about 3000 stores&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;EOY is about 5000 years&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Challenge: data platform cannot scale&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Retail part is around transaction data&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Pos Data set, 3rd party company&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;every transaction through api&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;POS their cloud -&amp;gt; each region has URL, - problem number 1 is 50 concurrent calls, batch,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Streaming endpoint, transaction files to object storage&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;challenge 2 - we read and process the data, consumer is store manager, What products are sold, what&#39;s in inventory, store manager looks and understand what inventory to fil, based on shopper schedule the resource, right now the transaction is now today 1 day, but we need with him 30 mins&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;1KB blob for sku, quantity, invoices, forecasting for every store, every SKU, same pipeline. Inventory system SaaS, bring the data for inventory, warehousing is also SaaS.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Foot traffic information - based days, based on SKU&#39;s sold.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;json files - from API, with store information, customer information, depends on api - batch mode,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;streaming is one json&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Security, Governance -&amp;gt; data access govern properly, Stores manager should see only their own, region manager only it&#39;s region, corp can see everything.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Stores in NA and Europe, Europe data in corp&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Lineage&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;DR - 1) Downtime should be 1 hour - RTO, RPO - cannot loose transaction, but reporting can be delayed.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Duplicates data - has to handled&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Observably - Yes&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Non functional - Small data engineering team - managing infra&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Infusing AI&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;5 years raw,&amp;nbsp; 3 years for reporting&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="650" width="650" x="70" y="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
